een%20contacted%20by%20people%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20claim%20is%20becoming%20increasingly%20global%20in%20scope...%20We%20expected%20that%20anywhere%20Mohamed%20Al-Fayed%20went%2C%20abuse%20would%20follow%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSadly%20this%20has%20proven%20to%20be%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20now%20in%20possession%20of%20credible%20evidence%20of%20abuse%20at%20other%20Al-Fayed%20properties%20and%20businesses%2C%20including%20Fulham%20Football%20Club.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBritish%20prosecutors%20have%20said%20they%20twice%20received%20evidence%20against%20Fayed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPattern%20of%20abuse%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202008%2C%20Fayed%20was%20accused%20of%20sexually%20assaulting%20a%2015-year-old%20girl%20and%20the%20Crown%20Prosecution%20Service%20(CPS)%20reviewed%20evidence%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20he%20was%20accused%20of%20raping%20a%20woman%2C%20a%20claim%20investigated%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20both%20instances%2C%20the%20CPS%2C%20which%20decides%20on%20prosecutions%20in%20England%20and%20Wales%2C%20said%20there%20was%20no%20%26quot%3Brealistic%20prospect%20of%20conviction%26quot%3B%20and%20did%20not%20bring%20charges%20against%20the%20Harrods%20chairman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyers%20said%20they%20would%20continue%20to%20respond%20to%20inquiries%20from%20potential%20victims%20or%20witnesses%20and%20called%20for%20an%20%26quot%3Bindependent%20and%20transparent%20process%20to%20evaluate%20and%20adjudicate%20these%20claims%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20women%20they%20represented%2C%20they%20said%2C%20had%20%26quot%3Blost%20all%20faith%20in%20Harrods%20and%20their%20processes%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarrods'%20managing%20director%2C%20Michael%20Ward%2C%20said%20this%20week%20his%20former%20boss%20presided%20over%20a%20%26quot%3Btoxic%20culture%20of%20se