d%20never%20forget%20and%20I%20wasn't%20allowed%20to.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20relationship%20became%20torturous.%20I%20had%20to%20prove%20my%20trustworthiness%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftimes-you-should-not-answer-your-phone-2017-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ealways%20answering%20my%20phone%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20or%20messages%20immediately.%20I%20had%20to%20throw%20out%20any%20clothes%20I%20might%20have%20worn%20during%20that%20period.%20My%20skin%20broke%20out%20worse%20than%20it%20ever%20had%20in%20my%20teens%20and%20I%20barely%20ate.%20The%20dramatic%20weight%20loss%20at%20least%20offered%20another%20way%20to%20maybe%20earn%20forgiveness%20because%20he%20had%20always%20liked%20thin%20girls.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESometimes%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-stop-recurring-nightmares-therapy-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI'd%20have%20nightmares%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20where%20I%20was%20shot%20and%2C%20as%20I%20fell%20to%20the%20ground%2C%20I'd%20cry%20because%20I%20was%20dying%20unabsolved.%20In%20other%20dreams%2C%20I'd%20be%20kissing%20a%20guy%20and%20then%20suddenly%20realize%20I%20actually%20had%20a%20boyfriend.%20I'd%20wake%20up%20panicking%20that%20I'd%20cheated%20again%20without%20meaning%20to.%20For%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20day%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20hiding%20more%20cheating%20and%20that%20the%20dream%20proved%20what%20I%20really%20was.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20following%20months%2C%20he%20would%20throw%20me%20out%20or%20I'd%20leave%20and%20go%20back%2C%20leave%20again%20and%20go%20back%20again.%20I%20lurched%20from%20one%20job%20to%20another%2C%20often%20quitting%20after%20a%20few%20weeks%20because%20I%20was%20too%20emotionally%20wrung%20out%20to%20function.%20I%20told%20elaborate%20lies%20to%20employers%20about%20why%20I%20was%20quitting.%20I%20moved%20a%20lot%2C%20always%20to%20places%20I%20knew%20no%20one%2C%20both%20as%20punishment%20and%20to%20hide%20away.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20one%20constant%20person%20in%20my%20life%20was%20my%20ex%20with%20whom%20I%20was%20still%20in%20regular%20contact%20even%20when%20he%20got%20a%20new%20girlfriend.%20I%20avoided%20old%20friends%20because%20I%20couldn't%20face%20anyone%20seeing%20how%20lost%20I%20was%20or%20who%20had%20known%20the%20old%20me.%20The%20cheating%20had%20defined%20me%20for%20so%20long%20I%20didn't%20know%20who%20I%20was.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223124c83d-e34e-4e96-8344-8d9cf5d0ac75%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20achieved%20self-forgiveness%20through%20a%20casual%20comment%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%20after%20another%20move%2C%20this%20time%20to%20Madrid%2C%20I%20met%20a%20guy%20I%20really%20liked.%20But%2C%20first%2C%20I%20had%20to%20confess%20so%20he%20could%20judge%20and%20decide%20whether%20to%20continue%20with%20me.%20To%20my%20surprise%2C%20he%20wasn't%20fazed%20at%20all.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BCheating%20isn't%20the%20worst%20thing%20you%20can%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20dismissing%20in%20seconds%20what%20had%20haunted%20me%20for%20three%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20disagreed%2C%20determined%20to%20stay%20penitent.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20worst%20thing%20you%20can%20do%20in%20a%20relationship%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20argued.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BOK%2C%20yes.%26quot%3B%20He%20shrugged.%20%26quot%3BBut%20no%20one%20died.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%2C%20in%20that%20moment%2C%20I%20forgave%20myself.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20wasn't%20about%20whether%20or%20not%20cheating%20was%20the%20biggest%20wrong%20you%20could%20do.%20It%20was%20that%20someone%20only%20saw%20me%2C%20not%20what%20I'd%