g%20vocal%20about.%20The%20thing%20about%20that%20show%20that%20it%20really%20taught%20me%20was%20just%20to%20be%20mindful%20when%20you%20sign%20a%20multi-year%20contract.%20That's%20it.%20That%20was%20my%20biggest%20takeaway%20from%20%26quot%3BSecret%20Life%26quot%3B%20was%20you%20sign%20a%20contract%2C%20and%20then%20there's%20legal%20responsibility.%20And%20I%20learned%20that%20lesson%20at%20a%20young%20age%2C%20which%20was%20a%20great%20lesson%20to%20learn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2238e72ffa-1593-4306-becf-4f48f0ca2941%5C%22%3EOn%20George%20Clooney's%20'magic%20heart%20of%20gold'%20and%20if%20she'd%20still%20do%20a%20fourth%20'Divergent'%20movie%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221998%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shailene%20Woodley%20and%20George%20Clooney%20at%20a%20photocall%20for%20%26quot%3BThe%20Descendants%26quot%3B%20in%20October%202011.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c8a505c72ebc54a40e4db0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221499%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWoodley%20and%20Clooney%20at%20a%20photocall%20for%20%26quot%3BThe%20Descendants%26quot%3B%20in%20October%202011.%3Cp%3EGareth%20Cattermole%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20the%20BFI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYour%20first%20big%20film%20role%20was%20%26quot%3BThe%20Descendants.%26quot%3B%20What%20was%20it%20like%20having%20George%20Clooney%20play%20your%20onscreen%20father%2C%20and%20what%20did%20you%20learn%20from%20working%20with%20a%20movie%20star%20like%20him%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%20for%20me%2C%20even%20though%20I%20started%20acting%20at%20such%20a%20young%20age%2C%20movies%20and%20TV%20were%20never%20really%20a%20part%20of%20my%20childhood.%20It%20could%20have%20been%20soccer%20or%20gymnastics%20that%20I%20was%20doing%20%E2%80%94%20it%20just%20happened%20to%20be%20film.%20No%20one%20in%20my%20family%20was%20in%20the%20industry%20at%20the%20time.%20And%20my%20brother%20and%20I%2C%20we%20didn't%20really%20watch%20many%20movies%20or%20TV%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20I%20met%20George%2C%20I%20had%20only%20ever%20seen%20%26quot%3BO%20Brother%2C%20Where%20Art%20Thou%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20knew%20he%20was%20famous%20because%20he's%20George%20Clooney%2C%20but%20I%20really%20didn't%20care%20at%20all.%20And%20because%20of%20that%2C%20I%20got%20to%20meet%20a%20dude%20who%20was%20kind%20and%20funny%20and%20courteous%20and%20had%20a%20magic%20heart%20of%20gold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20joke%2C%20I%20call%20him%20my%20old%20man%2C%20or%20he'll%20be%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20your%20old%20man.%26quot%3B%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20had%20an%20angel%20and%20a%20protector.%20I've%20been%20very%20lucky%2C%20actually%2C%20my%20whole%20career.%20Molly%20Ringwald%20did%20the%20same%20thing%20when%20I%20worked%20with%20her%2C%20and%20Ashley%20Judd%20and%20Kate%20Winslet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20I%20get%20emotional%20talking%20about%20George%20because%20I%20feel%20like%20he%20really...%20it%20makes%20me%20cry.%20He%20gave%20me%20the%20confidence%20to%20be%20exactly%20who%20I%20was%20in%20a%20world%20that%20so%20often%20tries%20to%20make%20you%20think%20that%20you%20need%20to%20be%20something%20that%20you're%20not%20in%20order%20to%20be%20successful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnother%20movie%20that's%20a%20touchstone%20of%20your%20career%20is%20the%20%26quot%3BDivergent%26quot%3B%20series.%20It's%20been%2010%20years.%20With%20all%20that%20time%2C%20is%20there%20anything%20that%20you%20look%20at%20differently%20about%20that%20franchise%20or%20your%20experience%20working%20on%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20when%20I%20got%20the%20offer.%20I%20was%20really%20scared%20to%20say%20yes%20because%20I%20had%20just%20gotten%20out%20of%20my%20contract%20with%20%26quot%3BSecret%20Life%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20here%20comes%20another%20multi-year%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EActing%2C%20for%20me%2C%20was%20a%20fun%20hobby.%20It%20still%20kind%20of%20feels%20that%2