gents%2C%20validating%20their%20charges%20of%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20sexual%20assault%2C%20and%20gender%20discrimination%2C%20including%20inferior%20job%20training%20and%20sales%20leads.%20BI%20has%20exclusively%20obtained%20copies%20of%20all%20of%20the%20letters%2C%20including%20ones%20addressed%20to%20Globe%20Life%2C%20American%20Income%20Life%2C%20and%20the%20Arias%20Organization%2C%20one%20of%20AIL's%20top%20agencies.%20The%20EEOC%20issues%20such%20letters%20when%20it%20has%20found%20evidence%20that%20discrimination%20has%20occurred.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20letters%2C%20the%20commission%20notes%20that%20Globe%2C%20AIL%2C%20and%20Arias%20have%20denied%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20morning%2C%20Globe%20filed%20a%20disclosure%20with%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20acknowledging%20receipt%20of%20the%20letters%20and%20saying%20the%20company%20disagrees%20with%20the%20commission's%20conclusions.%20Globe%20also%20said%20%26quot%3Bthe%20company%20has%20policies%20in%20place%20that%20prohibit%20discrimination%20of%20any%20form%20and%20takes%20allegations%20of%20such%20conduct%20seriously.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20found%20that%20Globe%2C%20AIL%2C%20and%20the%20Arias%20Organization%20have%20subjected%20an%20entire%20class%20of%20women%20to%20a%20hostile%20work%20environment%2C%20sexual%20quid%20pro%20quos%2C%20and%20retaliation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20repeated%20references%20in%20the%20letters%20to%20%26quot%3Ba%20class%20of%20female%20employees%26quot%3B%20could%20signal%20that%20the%20agency%20is%20laying%20the%20groundwork%20for%20a%20class-action%20lawsuit%2C%20according%20to%20Mark%20P.%20Carey%2C%20an%20employment%20attorney%20based%20in%20Southport%2C%20Connecticut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20like%20the%20EEOC%20is%20forming%20its%20own%20case%20against%20this%20employer%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Carey%2C%20whom%20BI%20briefed%20on%20the%20letters.%20%26quot%3BThis%20case%20is%20far%20from%20over.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20said%20it%20found%20violations%20nationwide%2C%20going%20back%20as%20far%20as%20January%201%2C%202011%2C%20and%20extending%20to%20the%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmerican%20Income%20Life%20is%20one%20of%20five%20wholly%20owned%20subsidiaries%20of%20Globe%20Life%20that%20sell%20life%2C%20accident%2C%20and%20supplemental%20health%20insurance.%20The%20abuses%20documented%20in%20the%20letters%20took%20place%20at%20the%20Wexford%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20headquarters%20of%20the%20Arias%20Organization%20and%20at%20Arias%20offices%20in%20multiple%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20finding%20that%20would%20be%20ominous%20for%20any%20company%20that%20relies%20heavily%20on%20contract%20workers%2C%20the%20EEOC%20said%20that%20Arias%20had%20misclassified%20a%20list%20of%20eight%20job%20titles%2C%20from%20caller%20to%20agent%20to%20state%20general%20agent%20%E2%80%94%20potentially%20the%20entirety%20of%20its%20US%20salesforce%20%E2%80%94%20as%20independent%20contractors.%20The%20company's%20%26quot%3Bcharacterization%20of%20its%20workers%20as%20'independent%20contractors'%20is%20inaccurate%2C%26quot%3B%20several%20of%20the%20letters%20reviewed%20by%20BI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20worker%20must%20be%20an%20employee%20in%20order%20to%20proceed%20with%20a%20discrimination%20claim%20at%20the%20EEOC%2C%20so%20the%20commission%20had%20to%20make%20this%20determination%20before%20proceeding%20with%20its%20sexual%20harassment%20investigation.%20In%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finvestors.globelifeinsurance.com%2Fannual-reports%2Fannual-reports%2F2023-annual-report-and-form-10k%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emost%20recent%3C%2Fa%3E%20annual%20report%2C%20Globe%20said%20that%20if%20the%20company%20were%20required%20to%20reclassify%20agents%20as%20employees%2C%20it%20%26quot%3Bcould%20significantly%20increase%20our%20operating%20costs%20and%20negatively%20impact%20our%20insurance%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20six%20women%20who%20received%20letters%20from%20the%20agency%20was%20Renee%20Zinsky%2C%20a%20former%20Arias%20agent%20at%20Wexford%20headquarters%20who%20alleged%20that%20her%20boss%2C%20a%20former%20Arias%20supervisor%20named%20Michael%20Russin%2C%20had%20sexually%20assaulted%20her%20and%20demanded%20sex%20in%20return%20for%20a%20promotion.%20BI%20was%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglobe-life-insurance-lawsuit-american-income-arias-agency-toxic-workplace-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20to%20report%20on%20Zinsky's%20claims%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20EEOC%20investigation%20confirmed%20her%20version%20of%20events%2C%20finding%20that%20she'd%20been%20subjected%20to%20nonconsensual%20touch%2C%20%26quot%3Bunwelcome%20displays%20of%20male%20genitalia%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bacts%20of%20male%20masturbation%20and%20pornography.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZinsky%20told%20BI%20on%20Thursday%20that%20it%20had%20been%20a%20%26quot%3Bbrutal%26quot%3B%20journey%20fighting%20Globe.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20never%20have%20thought%20that%20Arias%20and%20AIL%20would%20go%20to%20such%20lengths%20to%20continue%20to%20retaliate%20against%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20first%20step%20toward%20putting%20it%20all%20behind%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20woman%20who%20received%20a%20determination%20letter%2C%20Sarah%20Reay%2C%20who%20worked%20at%20an%20office%20in%20Morgantown%2C%20West%20Virginia%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20she%20had%20%26quot%3Bfelt%20defeated%26quot%3B%20after%20repeatedly%20reporting%20the%20discrimination%2C%20harassment%2C%20and%20fraud%20she%20experienced%2C%20%26quot%3Bjust%20to%20see%20the%20perpetrators%20be%20promoted.%26quot%3B%20It%20was%20a%20relief%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bto%20be%20finally%20heard%20and%20validated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20morning%2C%20BI%20reached%20out%20to%20Matthew%20D.%20Gailey%2C%20a%20lawyer%20for%20Russin%3B%20Arias%20spokeswoman%20Trina%20Orlando%3B%20Anne%20Rose%20Dana%20of%20King%20%26amp%3B%20Spalding%2C%20which%20represents%20AIL%3B%20and%20Globe%20Life%20spokeswoman%20Jennifer%20Haworth.%20None%20of%20them%20immediately%20responded%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20first%20wrote%20about%20the%20toxic%20workplace%20at%20the%20Arias%20Organization%2C%20then%20called%20Arias%20Agencies%2C%20in%20February%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglobe-life-insurance-lawsuit-american-income-arias-agency-toxic-workplace-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edescribing%20an%20intense%20masculine%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20violence%2C%20and%20drug%20use%20where%20agents%20would%20abuse%20customers%20and%20open%20accounts%20in%20the%20names%20of%20dead%20people%20in%20order%20to%20pocket%20a%20commission.%20BI's%20reporting%20showed%20that%20top%20executives%20at%20Globe%20and%20AIL%20lavished%20praise%20on%20Simon%20Arias%2C%20the%20agency's%20owner%2C%20who%20ran%20an%20operation%20where%20agents%20engaged%20openly%20in%20sexual%20harassment.%20At%20a%20Las%20Vegas%20convention%20in%202019%2C%20agents%20did%20drugs%20and%20had%20sex%20with%20one%20another%20while%20AIL's%20CEO%20and%20president%20partied%20with%20agents%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20subsequent%20articles%2C%20BI%20exposed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fracism-alleged-at-multiple-globe-life-affiliates-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20racist%20culture%20among%20top%20AIL%20managers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20launch%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdepartment-of-justice-probe-globe-life-american-income-life-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDepartment%20of%20Justice%20investigation%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20the%20Arias%20Organization%2C%20and%20the%20EEOC's%20decision%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feeoc-takes-up-sexual-harassment-cases-against-globe-life-subsidiary-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereopen%20two%20cases%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20Arias%20that%20it%20had%20previously%20closed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20BI's%20coverage%2C%20three%20prominent%20short-sellers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglobe-life-shares-crash-short-seller-reports-widespread-fraud-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eissued%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshort-seller-charges-globe-life-with-customer-deceit-worker-misclassification-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E%20marshaling%20further%20evidence%20of%20potentially%20illegal%20sales%20practices%2C%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20and%20drug%20use%20at%20AIL.%20One%20of%20them%2C%20Viceroy%20Research%2C%20also%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20misclassification%2C%20writing%20that%20Globe%20and%20AIL%20were%20calling%20agents%20independent%20contractors%20%26quot%3Bdespite%20having%20full%20control%20over%20their%20activities%20and%20enforcing%20non-competition%20clauses.%26quot%3B%20The%20Viceroy%20report%20saw%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20risk%26quot%3B%20that%20AIL%20would%20have%20to%20reclassify%20its%20agents%20and%20speculated%20that%20such%20a%20change%20could%20carry%20%26quot%3Ba%20deep%209-figure%20price%20tag.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20today's%20SEC%20filing%2C%20Globe%20said%20it%20did%20not%20believe%20the%20commission's%20enforcement%20actions%20would%20result%20in%20material%20loss%20to%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20April%2011%2C%20Globe's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglobe-life-timeline-explainer-federal-stock-price-fraud-investigation-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estock%20plunged%3C%2Fa%3E%2053%25%20after%20the%20short%20seller%20Fuzzy%20Panda%20released%20a%20report%20calling%20AIL%20a%20%26quot%3Bpyramid%20scheme%26quot%3B%20with%20an%20%26quot%3Bexhaustive%20array%20of%20financial%20malfeasance.%26quot%3B%20The%20stock%20has%20recovered%20most%20of%20its%20losses%2C%20helped%20in%20part%20by%20an%20aggressive%20stock%20buyback%20program%20by%20Globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGlobe's%20Audit%20Committee%20hired%20the%20law%20firm%20Wilmer%20Hale%20to%20conduct%20an%20internal%20audit%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20Fuzzy%20Panda%20report%3B%20the%20firm%20filed%20a%20statement%20with%20the%20SEC%20in%20July%20saying%20that%20the%20short-seller's%20allegations%20of%20financial%20misconduct%20were%20not%20supported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20an%20earnings%20call%20in%20July%2C%20Co-CEO%20Matt%20Darden%20said%20Globe%20%26quot%3Bhas%20reasonable%20and%20appropriate%20systems%20in%20place%20that%20are%20designed%20to%20detect%20and%20mitigate%20misconduct.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20EEOC%20came%20to%20a%20different%20conclusion.%20In%20the%20agency's%20letters%20yesterday%20to%20Zinsky%20and%20another%20woman%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglobe-life-arias-under-investigation-after-allegations-of-fraud-sexual-abuse-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAbeni%20Mayfield%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20former%20Arias%20agent%20in%20Columbia%2C%20Maryland%2C%20the%20commission%20said%20Globe%20had%20failed%20to%20implement%20or%20maintain%20%26quot%3Bany%20reasonably%20diligent%20sexual%20harassment%20policy%26quot%3B%20and%20to%20this%20day%20does%20not%20maintain%20%26quot%3Bany%20reasonable%20avenues%20for%20reporting%20sexual%20harassment%20or%20discrimination.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20July%20earnings%20call%2C%20Globe%20confirmed%20that%20two%20other%20federal%20agencies%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20and%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%20%E2%80%94%20were%20also%20investigating%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20EEOC%20said%20in%20its%20determination%20letters%20that%20it%20would%20be%20contacting%20the%20women%2C%20Globe%2C%20AIL%2C%20and%20the%20Arias%20Organization%20to%20begin%20a%20conciliation%20process%20in%20order%20to%20reach%20a%20settlement.%20Any%20settlement%2C%20according%20to%20the%20letters%2C%20signed%20by%20area%20director%20Deborah%20A.%20Kane%2C%20will%20require%20EEOC%20sign-off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20cases%20where%20conciliation%20fails%2C%20the%20EEOC%20sometimes%20files%20suit.%20Globe%20Life%20disclosed%20that%20risk%20in%20its%20filing%20this%20morning%20with%20the%20SEC%20and%20said%20it%20would%20fight%20any%20such%20lawsuit%20vigorously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmy%20Williamson%2C%20a%20Pittsburgh%20attorney%20who%20represents%20the%20six%20women%2C%20said%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20breath%20of%20fresh%20air%26quot%3B%20to%20have%20the%20agency%20involved%20after%20a%20grueling%20three%20years%20of%20litigation%20in%20the%20courts%20and%20in%20private%20arbitration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feeoc-finds-globe-life-created-hostile-work-environment-for-women-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727440364000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f6a09a75c877a99b61280e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feeoc-finds-globe-life-created-hostile-work-environment-for-women-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Globe%20Life%20and%20subsidiaries%20hit%20by%20EEOC%20investigation%3B%20the%20federal%20agency%20found%20rampant%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20gender%20discrimination.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22susan.antilla15%40gmail.com%20(Susan%20Antilla)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feeoc-finds-globe-life-created-hostile-work-environment-for-women-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sebi%20mulls%20standardise%20format%20for%20disclosure%20of%20change%20in%20MF%20risk-o-meters%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%