0the%20two%20tallest%20leaders%20of%20the%20party%20in%20the%20state%20will%20be%20lasting%20and%20result%20in%20victory%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Chance%20For%20Rahul%20To%20Cement%20His%20Glory%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20various%20reasons%2C%20Haryana%20is%20going%20to%20be%20the%20litmus%20test%20not%20only%20for%20the%20Congress%20but%20also%20for%20Rahul.%20This%20year's%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20gave%20a%20new%20lease%20of%20life%20to%20him.%20His%20party%20improved%20its%20seat%20tally%20from%2052%20to%2099%2C%20with%20the%20credit%20for%20this%20boost%20going%20mostly%20to%20Rahul.%20His%20status%20in%20the%20party%20as%20its%20most%20significant%20leader%2C%20which%20was%20in%20doubt%20since%20the%202019%20elections%2C%20has%20finally%20been%20cemented.%20The%20days%20of%20'G23'%20in%20the%20Congress%20are%20over.%20Rahul%20now%20has%20the%20final%20word%20on%20party%20matters.%20He%20is%20also%20informally%20treated%20as%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20entire%20opposition.%20In%20that%20sense%2C%20a%20victory%20in%20Haryana%20will%20further%20bolster%20his%20image%20as%20the%20new%20mass%20base%20leader%20in%20Indian%20politics%20and%20a%20worthy%20challenger%20to%20Modi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party's%20(BJP)%20performance%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20Haryana%20was%20dismal.%20It%20could%20win%20only%20five%20seats%20out%20of%2010%2C%20and%20its%20vote%20share%20dropped%20by%2012%20percentage%20points%20vis%20a%20vis%20the%20last%20parliamentary%20election.%20Back%20then%2C%20in%202019%2C%20the%20vote%20share%20gap%20between%20the%20two%20parties%20had%20been%20a%20whopping%2030%25.%20But%20in%20the%20assembly%20election%20that%20took%20place%20after%20three%20months%2C%20the%20BJP%20failed%20to%20get%20a%20majority%20mark%20and%20had%20to%20take%20the%20support%20of%20the%20Jannayak%20Janta%20Party%20(JJP)%2C%20which%20had%20severely%20criticised%20PM%20Modi%20earlier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20BJP%20Is%20Struggling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20second%20term%20in%20the%20state%20has%20been%20disappointing%2C%20to%20say%20the%20least.%20The%20party's%20high%20command%20had%20to%20replace%20Chief%20Minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20at%20the%20last%20minute.%20Today%2C%20his%20face%20is%20missing%20from%20the%20party's%20publicity%20material.%20The%20new%20chief%20minister%2C%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%2C%20seems%20equally%20ineffective.%20The%20BJP%20seems%20to%20be%20struggling%20in%20this%20election%20and%20it%20will%20be%20a%20miracle%20if%20it%20turns%20the%20table%20on%20counting%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Haryana%20is%20singularly%20important%20for%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20In%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20a%20junior%20partner.%20It%20is%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20National%20Conference%20and%20is%20contesting%20only%2032%20seats%2C%20mostly%20in%20the%20Jammu%20region.%20The%20BJP%20is%20not%20a%20major%20player%20in%20the%20Valley%20either%20and%20is%20banking%20on%20independents%20and%20smaller%20parties.%20Given%20that%20this%20will%20be%20the%20first%20assembly%20election%20in%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20after%20the%20abrogation%20of%20articles%20370%20and%2035A%2C%20the%20Modi%20government's%20prestige%20is%20at%20stake.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBitter%20Past%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Haryana%20is%20a%20different%20ballgame.%20For%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20state%20has%20made%20news%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%20for%20all%20the%20wrong%20reasons.%20It%20turned%20into%20a%20battleground%20during%20the%20farmer's%20movement%20and%20after%20over%20a%20year%20of%20discontent%2C%20PM%20Modi%20had%20to%20withdraw%20the%20three%20farm%20laws.%20But%20the%20treatment%20meted%20out%20to%20the%20farmers%20and%20attempts%20to%20paint%20them%20as%20'Khalistanis'%20made%20them%20bitter.%20Their%20anger%20is%20still%20intact%20in%20many%20places%20in%20the%20state's%20rural%20areas%20and%20there%20are%20reports%20that%20BJP%20candidates%20are%20either%20being%20gheraoed%20or%20being%20chased%20away%20in%20several%20villages.%20Rahul%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20squarely%20blamed%20Modi%20for%20the%20ill-treatment.%20He%20has%20also%20promised%20that%20if%20the%20Congress%20forms%20a%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20then%20the%20party%20would%20give%20legal%20guarantees%20of%20MSP%2C%20one%20of%20the%20main%20demands%20of%20farmers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20of%20Haryana%20are%20also%20anguished%20over%20the%20way%20women%20wrestlers%20protesting%20against%20alleged%20sexual%20harassment%20by%20BJP%20MP%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Singh%20were%20treated%20by%20the%20BJP%20government.%20It%20was%20only%20after%20the%20intervention%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20an%20FIR%20was%20registered%20against%20Singh.%20These%20girls%20were%20so%20disappointed%20that%20they%20even%20decided%20to%20throw%20their%20medals%20in%20the%20Ganga.%20No%20arrest%20was%20made%20and%20though%20he%20was%20denied%20a%20party%20ticket%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20Singh's%20son%20contested%20elections%20as%20a%20proxy.%20When%20Vignesh%20Phogat%20and%20Bajrang%20Punia%20joined%20the%20Congress%2C%20a%20few%20BJP%20leaders%20accused%20them%20of%20a%20conspiracy.%20In%20this%20light%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Haryana%2C%20specifically%20the%20Jat%20community%2C%20believe%20that%20the%20BJP%20did%20not%20take%20any%20action%20against%20Singh%20because%20it%20was%20scared%20of%20losing%20a%20few%20seats%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20did%20not%20want%20to%20annoy%20the%20Rajput%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20strategy%20since%20it%20came%20to%20power%20in%202014%20was%20to%20polarise%20other%20castes%20against%20the%20Jat%20community%2C%20to%20which%20a%20majority%20of%20protesting%20wrestlers%20also%20belong.%20In%20fact%2C%20ignoring%20the%20Jat%20leaders'%20demands%2C%20the%20party%20appointed%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%2C%20a%20Punjabi%2C%20as%20the%20chief%20minister.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Defeat%20Can%20Confuse%20Congress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20supported%20the%20wrestlers'%20cause%20from%20the%20beginning.%20A%20victory%20for%20the%20Congress%20will%20raise%20his%20stature%20in%20the%20community.%20A%20loss%20will%20send%20a%20wrong%20signal%20and%20will%20lead%20to%20the%20marginalisation%20of%20the%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20his%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20strong%20challenger%20to%20Modi's%20politics.%20He%20has%20also%20very%20strongly%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20social%20justice%20and%20caste%20census.%20He%20is%20weaving%20a%20parallel%20narrative%20against%20the%20BJP's%20Hindutva%20and%20nationalism%20plans%20and%20has%20accused%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20of%20pursuing%20divisive%20politics%20and%20dividing%20society%20on%20religious%20lines.%20There%20are%20trends%20that%20show%20that%20his%20politics%2C%20like%20in%20South%20India%2C%20have%20traction%20in%20north%20Indian%20states%20too.%20Even%20in%20Haryana%2C%20he%20is%20very%20close%20to%20Modi%20in%20terms%20of%20popularity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0If%20the%20Congress%20wins%20Haryana%20with%20a%20big%20margin%2C%20then%20it%20will%20be%20a%20big%20stamp%20of%20approval%20to%20Rahul's%20politics%20of%20secularism%20and%20his%20recent%20experiment%20with%20social%20justice.%20A%20loss%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20will%20bring%20confusion%20in%20the%20Congress%20ranks.%20It%20will%20also%20break%20the%20momentum%20that%20Rahul%20and%20his%20party%20have%20attained%20since%20the%20parliamentary%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20in%20this%20context%20that%20bringing%20two%20warring%20factions%20in%20Haryana%20on%20the%20same%20platform%20is%20good%20for%20both%20Rahul%20and%20the%20Congress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Ashutosh%20is%20the%20author%20of%20'Hindu%20Rashtra'%20and%20co-founder%20of%C2%A0SatyaHindi.com)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727438400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F0rp2l6po_rahul-gandhi_625x300_27_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fharyana-will-be-a-litmus-test-for-both-rahul-and-congress-6662765%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20the%20Congress%20wins%20Haryana%20with%20a%20big%20margin%2C%20then%20it%20will%20be%20a%20big%20stamp%20of%20approval%20to%20Rahul's%20politics%20of%20secularism%20and%20his%20recent%20experiment%20with%20social%20justice.%20A%20loss%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20will%20bring%20confusion%20in%20the%20Congress%20ranks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fharyana-will-be-a-litmus-test-for-both-rahul-and-congress-6662765%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Katy%20Perry%2C%20Tate%20McRae%2C%20Jack%20Harlow%20Lead%20iHeartRadio%20Jingle%20Ball%202024%20Tour%20Lineups%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727438400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fiheart-e1727397083112.jpg%3Fcrop%3D0px%252C17px%252C1773px%252C1013px%26resize%3D1000%252C563%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236157560%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Katy%20Perry%2C%20Tate%20McRae%20and%20Jack%20Harlow%20are%20just%20a%20few%20of%20the%20acts%20scheduled%20to%20perform%20as%20part%20of%20iHeartRadio%E2%80%99s%20Jingle%20Ball%20Tour%202024%2C%20presented%20by%20Capital%20One.%20Additional%20artists%20slated%20to%20join%20the%20various%20lineups%20across%20the%