20Fan%20During%20Kanpur%20Test%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETiger%20Robi%2C%20a%20Bangladeshi%20supporter%20who%20was%20allegedly%20beaten%20and%20heckled%20in%20the%20second%20Test%20match%20between%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%2C%20is%20said%20to%20be%20fine%20and%20was%20taken%20to%20hospital%20for%20a%20checkup%2C%20confirmed%20UP%20Police.%20Robi%2C%20a%20fan%20from%20Dhaka%2C%20was%20allegedly%20beaten%20and%20heckled%20by%20spectators%20at%20Green%20Park%20Stadium%20and%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20Regency%20Hospital%20by%20the%20police.%20According%20to%20a%20statement%20by%20a%20police%20official%20at%20the%20stadium%2C%20Robi%20had%20been%20feeling%20unwell%20before%20arriving%20and%20fainted%20due%20to%20the%20heat%20in%20the%20unauthorised%20C-upper%20stand%2C%20which%20had%20been%20closed%20by%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Cricket%20Association%20(UPCA)%20over%20structural%20concerns.%20%26quot%3BHe%20is%20fine%20now%2C%20and%20we%20took%20him%20to%20Regency%20Hospital%20for%20a%20check-up.%20There%20was%20no%20assault%2C%20just%20a%20case%20of%20heat%20exhaustion%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20occurred%20during%20the%20first%20session%20of%20the%20match%20when%20Robi%20was%20seen%20waving%20a%20Bangladeshi%20flag%20from%20the%20unauthorised%20stand.%20This%20reportedly%20sparked%20a%20confrontation%20with%20some%20Indian%20spectators.%20Tensions%20escalated%2C%20and%20security%20personnel%20intervened%20to%20diffuse%20the%20situation.%20However%2C%20Robi%20later%20alleged%20that%20during%20the%20lunch%20break%2C%20a%20group%20of%20local%20fans%20physically%20assaulted%20him.'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20match%2C%C2%A0%C2%A0Bangladesh%C2%A0were%20107%20for%203%20in%2035%20overs%20when%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20second%20Test%20between%20India%20and%C2%A0Bangladesh%C2%A0at%20Green%20Park%20Stadium%20was%20called%20off%20due%20to%20rain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20delayed%20start%20due%20to%20a%20wet%20outfield%2C%20India%20capitalised%20on%20seam-friendly%20conditions%20early%20on%2C%20but%20the%20visitors%20slowly%20clawed%20their%20way%20back%20into%20the%20contest%2C%20thanks%20to%20a%20promising%20partnership%20between%20Najmul%20Hossain%20Shanto%20and%20Mominul%20Haque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20Sharma's%20decision%20to%20bowl%20first%20paid%20off%20immediately%20as%20India's%20pacer%20Akash%20Deep%2C%20who%20has%20been%20on%20a%20roll%2C%20made%20early%20inroads.%20He%20struck%20twice%20in%20his%20first%20spell%2C%20leaving%C2%A0Bangladesh%C2%A0at%2033%2F2.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZakir%20Hasan%20fell%20for%20a%20duck%2C%20undone%20by%20a%20beautiful%20delivery%20from%20Akash%20that%20angled%20in%20and%20shaped%20away%20late%2C%20edging%20to%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20at%20gully%20for%20a%20stunning%20low%20catch.%20Shadnam%20Islam%20followed%20soon%20after%2C%20trapped%20lbw%20by%20Akash%20in%20a%20decision%20that%20was%20initially%20given%20not%20out%20but%20overturned%20upon%20review%2C%20thanks%20to%20Rohit's%20smart%20use%20of%20DRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBangladesh%C2%A0were%20reeling%20at%2078%2F2%20by%20lunch%20with%20their%20hopes%20for%20recovery%20rested%20on%20their%20captain%20Shanto%20and%20the%20experienced%20Mominul%20Haque.%20Both%20batters%20weathered%20the%20Indian%20pace%20attack%2C%20with%20Mominul%20gradually%20finding%20his%20rhythm%20and%20displaying%20some%20lovely%20stroke%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShanto%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20played%20with%20solid%20technique%20to%20grind%20out%20runs%20on%20a%20pitch%20that%20appeared%20to%20be%20flattening%20out%20as%20the%20day%20progressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20wasn't%20long%20before%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20worked%20his%20magic.%20India's%20ace%20off-spinner%20broke%20through%20Shanto's%20resistance%20with%20a%20clever%20arm-ball%2C%20luring%20the%C2%A0Bangladeshi%20skipper%20into%20playing%20for%20spin%20before%20trapping%20him%20lbw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShanto's%20dismissal%20for%2031%2C%20just%20when%20he%20seemed%20set%20to%20anchor%20the%20innings%2C%20was%20a%20blow%20to%C2%A0Bangladesh's%20hopes.%20Mushfiqur%20Rahim%20was%20then%20tasked%20with%20steadying%20the%20ship%20alongside%20Mominul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20afternoon%20session%20saw%C2%A0Bangladesh%C2%A0show%20signs%20of%20recovery%2C%20with%20Mominul%20playing%20some%20aggressive%20shots%2C%20including%20a%20couple%20of%20boundaries%2C%20to%20relieve%20the%20pressure.%20The%20pitch%2C%20though%20unpredictable%20earlier%2C%20seemed%20to%20ease%20for%20batting%20as%20the%20day%20wore%20on.%20But%20just%20as%20momentum%20began%20to%20swing%20toward%C2%A0Bangladesh%2C%20bad%20light%20interrupted%20play%20and%20persistent%20drizzle%2C%20forcing%20an%20early%20end%20to%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20early%20stoppage%20was%20a%20relief%20for%20India%2C%20as%20the%C2%A0Bangladeshi%20middle%20order%2C%20led%20by%20Mominul%2C%20was%20starting%20to%20assert%20itself.%20Mominul%20remained%20unbeaten%20on%2040%2C%20with%20Mushfiqur%20at%20the%20other%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727438040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F529e8kro_cs_625x300_27_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-bangladesh-2024%2Fjust-a-case-of-up-police-on-row-over-bangladesh-super-fan-during-kanpur-test-6662242%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tiger%20Robi%2C%20a%20Bangladeshi%20supporter%20who%20was%20allegedly%20beaten%20and%20heckled%20in%20the%20second%20Test%20match%20between%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%2C%20is%20said%20to%20be%20fine%20and%20was%20taken%20to%20hospital%20for%20a%20checkup%2C%20confirmed%20UP%20Police.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-bangladesh-2024%2Fjust-a-case-of-up-police-on-row-over-bangladesh-super-fan-during-kanpur-test-6662242%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%2