ng%20a%20loved%20one%20while%20also%20grappling%20with%20a%20lack%20of%20insurance%20for%20my%20dad's%20end-of-life%20expenses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%20ordeal%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20up%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Flife-insurance%2Fbest-life-insurance-companies%5C%22%3Elife%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20ensure%20that%20my%20family%20wouldn't%20face%20the%20same%20troubles%20if%20I%20died%20unexpectedly.%20It%20was%20important%20to%20me%20that%20%E2%80%94%20on%20top%20of%20paying%20funeral%20costs%20%E2%80%94%20my%20life%20insurance%20policy%20also%20covered%20our%20home's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fbest-mortgage-lenders%5C%22%3Emortgage%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20realized%20I%20didn't%20feel%20ready%20for%20a%20worst-case%20scenario%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20shopping%20around%20and%20finding%20a%20plan%20that%20worked%20for%20me%2C%20I%20felt%20prepared%20enough%20to%20forget%20about%20life%20insurance.%20However%2C%20an%20emergency%20hernia%20surgery%20exposed%20hidden%20health%20concerns%20that%20made%20me%20reassess%20my%20coverage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20developed%20an%20umbilical%20hernia%20that%20needed%20immediate%20surgery%20to%20avoid%20more%20damage.%20The%20operation%20was%20pretty%20uneventful%2C%20and%20life%20went%20back%20to%20normal%20soon%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20routine%20appointment%20with%20my%20rheumatologist%20a%20few%20months%20later%2C%20I%20got%20a%20concerning%20surprise.%20In%20reviewing%20scans%20from%20before%20my%20surgery%2C%20my%20rheumatologist%20spotted%20an%20unexpected%20irregularity.%20The%20scans%20suggested%20that%20I%20might%20have%20lymphoma%2C%20a%20type%20of%20blood%20cancer%20that%20affects%20the%20immune%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20followed%20was%20two%20months%20of%20scans%2C%20blood%20tests%2C%20biopsies%2C%20meetings%20with%20oncologists%2C%20and%20overwhelming%20anxiety.%20In%20my%20need%20to%20plan%20for%20the%20worst%2C%20I%20looked%20into%20my%20life%20insurance%20and%20bumped%20it%20up%20to%20%24500%2C000%2C%20but%20I%20still%20felt%20unprepared%20for%20a%20cancer%20diagnosis.%20I%20started%20planning%20for%20the%20worst-case%20scenario%2C%20but%20I%20feared%20that%20no%20matter%20what%20I%20did%2C%20it%20wouldn't%20be%20enough%20to%20put%20me%20at%20ease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20long%2C%20stressful%20process%2C%20I%20finally%20got%20my%20results%20back.%20My%20biopsy%20thankfully%20came%20back%20cancer-free!%20However%2C%20my%20good%20news%20also%20came%20with%20some%20bad.%20I%20learned%20that%20the%20inflammation%20to%20my%20lymph%20nodes%20that%20showed%20up%20on%20my%20scans%20was%20due%20to%20my%20chronic%20autoimmune%20disease.%20And%2C%20because%20of%20that%20chronic%20inflammation%2C%20my%20chances%20of%20one%20day%20developing%20lymphoma%20are%20twice%20as%20likely%20as%20someone%20without%20an%20autoimmune%20disease.%20Even%20though%20I'm%20currently%20cancer-free%2C%20an%20increased%20likelihood%20of%20cancer%20looms%20ahead%20in%20my%20future%2C%20and%20I%20refuse%20to%20be%20caught%20unawares%20yet%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EGetting%20cancer%20insurance%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20through%20my%20life%20insurance%20research%20that%20I%20found%20exactly%20what%20I%20needed%20to%20feel%20prepared%20should%20I%20have%20to%20face%20cancer%20head-on.%20Some%20insurance%20companies%20offer%20cancer%20insurance%2C%20which%20covers%20several%20costs%20associated%20with%20cancer%20treatment%20and%20pays%20out%20a%20set%20amount%20to%20the%20policyholder%20to%20help%20cover%20these%20expenses.%20I%20signed%20up%20for%20cancer%20insurance%20with%20Aflac.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20start%20of%20my%20insurance%20journey%2C%20I%20was%20only%20really%20familiar%20with%20health%20and%20life%20insurance%2C%20so%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20find%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Flife-insurance%2Fwhat-is-supplemental-life-insurance%5C%22%3Esupplemental%20life%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20specifically%20footed%20the%20bill%20for%20costs%20related%20to%20cancer.%20Unlike%20critical%20illness%20insurance%2C%20cancer%20insurance%20only%20covers%20costs%20associated%20with%20cancer.%20Still%2C%20the%20more%20I%20learned%2C%20the%20more%20I%20realized%20that%20cancer%20insurance%20was%20exactly%20what%20I%20needed%20to%20ease%20my%20concerns%20about%20preparing%20for%20the%20worst.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20any%20major%20disease%2C%20there%20are%20costs%20associated%20with%20cancer.%20Expenses%20for%20tests%20and%20treatments%2C%20loss%20of%20wages%20because%20of%20illness%2C%20and%20travel%20costs%20for%20medical%20care%20are%20just%20some%20of%20the%20extra%20financial%20penalties%20that%20follow%20cancer%20patients.%20This%20surprise%20expense%20sometimes%20keeps%20cancer%20patients%20from%20getting%20the%20care%20and%20treatment%20they%20need.%20A%20plan%20that%20helps%20me%20cover%20these%20expenses%20in%20the%20event%20that%20I%20develop%20cancer%20is%20a%20godsend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMy%20policy%20covers%20me%20even%20before%20a%20diagnosis%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20cancer%20insurance%20plan%20through%20Aflac%2C%20support%20is%20offered%20even%20before%20a%20diagnosis.%20The%20plan%20pays%20out%20funds%20to%20be%20used%20for%20preventive%20coverage%20in%20the%20form%20of%20tests%2C%20scans%2C%20and%20biopsies%20that%20are%20designed%20to%20detect%20cancer%20early%20on.%20There%20is%20also%20coverage%20payout%20for%20preventive%20surgery%20associated%20with%20positive%20genetic%20test%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20plan%20offers%20an%20initial%20payout%20in%20the%20case%20of%20a%20cancer%20diagnosis%20and%20offers%20funds%20to%20pay%20for%20a%20second%20opinion%20if%20desired.%20Ambulance%20rides%2C%20lodging%2C%20and%20transportation%20are%20also%20considered%20in%20the%20plan%2C%20offering%20compensation%20for%20these%20costs%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20different%20health%20insurance%20plans%20offer%20different%20treatment%20coverages%2C%20Aflac's%20cancer%20insurance%20offers%20supplemental%20coverage%20that%20covers%20several%20treatment%20options.%20From%20radiation%20therapy%2C%20chemotherapy%2C%20and%20immunotherapy%20to%20stem%20cell%20and%20bone%20marrow%20transplants%2C%20there's%20no%20lack%20of%20care%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20coverage%20for%20life%20after%20cancer%2C%20with%20funds%20that%20can%20be%20used%20for%20reconstructive%20surgery%2C%20prosthetics%2C%20and%20reproductive%20services.%20In%20the%20unfortunate%20case%20of%20a%20terminal%20diagnosis%2C%20my%20policy%20also%20covers%20home%20healthcare%2C%20private%20nurse%20services%2C%20and%20hospice%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20know%20where%20to%20start%20with%20your%20finances%3F%20Consider%20a%20financial%20advisor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fretirement%2Ffind-a-financial-planner%3Futm_source%3Dbusinessinsider%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dbus__falc_bicontent%26utm_content%3DBI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinding%20a%20financial%20advisor%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20hard.%20SmartAsset's%20free%20tool%20matches%20you%20with%20up%20to%20three%20fiduciary%20financial%20advisors%20who%20serve%20your%20area%20in%20minutes.%20Each%20advisor%20has%20been%20vetted%20by%20SmartAsset%20and%20is%20held%20to%20a%20fiduciary%20standard%20to%20act%20in%20your%20best%20interests.%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fretirement%2Ffind-a-financial-planner%3Futm_source%3Dbusinessinsider%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dbus__falc_bicontent%26utm_content%3DBI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Start%20your%20search%20now.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%2