%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fbhool-bhulaiyaa-3-teaser-x-reactions-fans-celebrate-vidya-balans-return-as-manjulika%2Farticleshow%2F113739531.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20Fell...%26quot%3B%3A%20BAN%20Super%20Fan%20Changes%20Tune%20Amid%20Assault%20Row%20During%20Kanpur%20Test%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Bangladeshi%20cricket%20fan%20had%20to%20be%20hospitalised%20after%20%26quot%3Bfalling%20ill%26quot%3B%20while%20watching%20the%20second%20Test%20against%20India%20at%20the%20Green%20Park%20Stadium%20in%20Kanpur%2C%20an%20incident%20that%20was%20first%20suspected%20to%20be%20a%20case%20of%20heckling%20after%20he%20indicated%20being%20involved%20in%20a%20physical%20altercation.%20Self-proclaimed%20super%20fan%20Roby%2C%20who%20dresses%20in%20tiger%20costume%20and%20is%20a%20regular%20in%20his%20team's%20games%2C%20was%20in%20stand%20C%20and%20had%20to%20be%20carried%20out%20of%20the%20stadium%20in%20a%20state%20of%20distress.%20During%20a%20brief%20interaction%20with%20media%2C%20Roby%20indicated%20that%20he%20had%20been%20punched%20in%20his%20abdomen%20during%20an%20altercation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20a%20statement%20issued%20from%20his%20hospital%20bed%20later%2C%20he%20said%20he%20merely%20felt%20unwell%20and%20was%20given%20the%20requisite%20assistance%20by%20the%20local%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20fell%20ill%20and%20the%20police%20brought%20me%20to%20the%20hospital.%20Now%20I%20am%20feeling%20much%20better.%20My%20name%20is%20Roby%20and%20I%20have%20come%20from%20Bangladesh%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stated%20in%20a%20short%20video%20clip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhishek%20Pandey%2C%20ACP%20(Kalyanpur)%2C%20said%20Roby%20received%20immediate%20medical%20care%20and%20insisted%20that%20he%20had%20not%20been%20assaulted%20as%20alleged%20in%20early%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20Test%20matc