22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fbhool-bhulaiyaa-3-teaser-madhuri-dixits-absence-sparks-speculation-about-her-role-in-the-film%2Farticleshow%2F113738067.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHas%20Not%20Performed%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20Blasts%20Delhi%20Air%20Quality%20Panel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20central%20air%20quality%20panel%20on%20Friday%20for%20not%20taking%20adequate%20steps%20to%20monitor%20the%20air%20quality%20and%20curb%20pollution%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20region.%20The%20Commission%20for%20Air%20Quality%20Management%20(CAQM)%20has%20not%20performed%20or%20served%20its%20purpose%2C%20a%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Abhay%20S%20Oka%20and%20AG%20Masih%20said%20in%20a%20series%20of%20tough%20observations%20as%20Delhi%20and%20its%20surrounding%20areas%20approach%20pollution%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20has%20been%20total%20non-compliance%20of%20the%20Act.%20Have%20committees%20been%20constituted%3F%20Please%20show%20us%20a%20single%20step%20taken%2C%20which%20directions%20have%20you%20used%20under%20the%20Act%3F%20Just%20see%20the%20affidavit.%20Show%20us%20a%20single%20direction%20issued%20under%20S%2012%20and%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Justice%20Oka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20all%20in%20the%20air%2C%20nothing%20they%20have%20showed%20as%20to%20what%20they%20have%20said%20to%20the%20NCR%20States%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETowards%20the%20end%20of%20the%20hearing%2C%20the%20bench%20noted%20that%20it%20cannot%20be%20said%20that%20the%20CAQM%20did%20not%20take%20any%20action%2C%20but%20they%20did%20not%20perform%20the%20way%20they%20were%20expected%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECome%20winter%2C%20the%20NCR%20plunges%20into%20a%20severe%20air%20quality%20crisis%20every%20year%2C%20with%20stubble%20burn%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20states%20of%20Haryana%20and%20Punjab%20among%20the%20major%20contributors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20informed%20by%20CAQM%20chairman%20Rajesh%20Verma%20that%20they%20meet%20once%20in%20three%20months%2C%20the%20court%20sought%20to%20know%20if%20that's%20enough%2C%20if%20decisions%20taken%20by%20them%20have%20helped%20in%20solving%20problems%2C%20and%20if%20incidents%20of%20stubble%20burning%20are%20coming%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20also%20asked%20the%20chairman%20what%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20against%20erring%20officials.%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20Aishwarya%20Bhati%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Centre%2C%20said%20that%20the%20chairman%20had%20joined%20only%20two%20weeks%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAQM%20chairman%20also%20informed%20that%20meetings%20were%20held%20with%20the%20officials%20and%20pollution%20board%20of%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%2C%20and%20they%20have%20issued%20warnings%20to%20their%20chief%20secretaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Aprajita%20Singh%2C%20assisting%20the%20court%20as%20amicus%20curiae%2C%20said%20if%20their%20law%20was%20being%20violated%2C%20they%20have%20the%20authority%20to%20take%20action.%20%26quot%3BBut%20they%20are%20being%20silent%20spectators%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Singh%20said%20thousands%20of%20crores%20were%20offered%20to%20the%20farmers%20for%20equipment%20to%20help%20stop%20stubble%20burning.%20%26quot%3BIn%202017%2C%20we%20thought%20it%20would%20help%20stop%2C%20but%20it%20has%20not%20and%20that%20is%20why%20the%20CAQM%20has%20come%20today%20and%20now%20some%20officer%20has%20to%20be%20held%20responsible%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20efforts%20must%20be%20taken%20to%20ensure%20the%20use%20of%20stubble-burning%20alternatives%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20duties%20is%20to%20work%20with%20NCR%20States%20and%20it%20(CAQM)%20has%20vast%20powers%20conferred%20including%20closure%20of%20polluting%20units.%20We%20are%20of%20the%20view%20that%20though%20the%20Commission%20has%20taken%20certain%20steps%2C%20the%20Commission%20needs%20to%20be%20more%20active%20and%20must%20ensure%20that%20its%20efforts%20and%20directions%20actually%20translate%20into%20reducing%20the%20problem%20of%20pollution%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20asked%20the%20CAQM%20to%20submit%20the%20details%20of%20their%20meetings%20and%20a%20better%20compliance%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20will%20be%20heard%20again%20next%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727433300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F29gj1jdo_delhi-pollution-afp_625x300_18_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fall-in-the-air-supreme-court-comes-down-heavily-on-delhi-air-quality-panel-6661776%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20central%20air%20quality%20panel%20on%20Friday%20for%20not%20taking%20steps%20to%20monitor%20the%20air%20quality%20and%20curb%20pollution%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20region.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fall-in-the-air-supreme-court-comes-down-heavily-on-delhi-air-quality-panel-6661776%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2215-year-old%20boy%20cycles%2058km%20in%207%20hours%20to%20see%20Kohli%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727433145000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113737925%2Cimgsize-57854.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fbangladesh-in-india%2F58-km-in-7-hours-15-year-old-boy-cycles-from-unnao-to-kanpur-to-watch-virat-kohli-bat%2Farticleshow