t%20sustainability%20at%20the%20fore%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELed%20by%20Malik%20Architecture%2C%20the%20team%20embarked%20on%20the%20quest%20to%20give%20the%20ice%20factory%20a%20second%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20IF.BE%20is%20a%2010%2C000-square-foot%20space%20that%20boasts%20five%20sections%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%98The%20Banyan%20Tree%20Caf%C3%A9%E2%80%99%3B%20%E2%80%98The%20Substation%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F145074%2Flibrary-books-ruchi-dhona-children-education%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereading%20room%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20shop%20for%20architectural%20instruments%20and%20books%3B%20the%20%E2%80%98Ice%20Factory%E2%80%99%20designed%20for%20performances%3B%20%E2%80%98The%20Cathedral%E2%80%99%20where%20the%20bulk%20of%20exhibitions%20take%20place%3B%20and%20the%20fine%20dining%20Indian%20restaurant%2C%20Native%20Bombay%2C%20where%20guests%20fuel%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIF.BE%3A%20Stitching%20sustainability%20with%20history%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20name%20of%20the%20project%20and%20the%20addition%20of%20the%20dot%20between%20the%20words%20does%20not%20skip%20my%20attention.%20Elaborating%20on%20it%2C%20Malik%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20dot%20%E2%80%94%20that%20gap%20between%20%E2%80%98if%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98be%E2%80%99%20symbolises%20time.%20If%20and%20be%20%E2%80%94%20the%20possibilities.%E2%80%9D%20And%20this%20is%20essentially%20the%20message%20that%20the%20architects%20have%20attempted%20to%20convey%2C%20the%20freedom%20that%20comes%20with%20the%20arts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Malik%20details%20the%20restoration%2C%20one%20thing%20is%20evident%3A%20the%20rendering%20was%20rooted%20in%20honest%20appreciation%20of%20the%20building%E2%80%99s%20history.%20The%20end%20goal%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20simply%20aesthetics%2C%20but%20to%20preserve%20the%20antiquity%20of%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FwxqELyjGVzc%3Fsi%3D89ZvtAppDdIJ199C%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2030%20months%20of%20%E2%80%9Cpainstaking%20efforts%E2%80%9D%20were%20directed%20towards%20retaining%20existing%20details%20that%20played%20a%20role%20in%20the%20building%E2%80%99s%20legacy%2C%20in%20a%20more%20nuanced%20fashion.%20Malik%20adds%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332749%2Fex-banker-sunando-sen-built-tanhau-sustainable-himalayan-homestay-corbett-restore-wildlife%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etouches%20of%20sustainability%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20included%20in%20every%20way%20possible.%20For%20months%2C%20the%20team%20scraped%20away%20at%20old%20plaster%2C%20which%20yielded%20brickwork%20and%20vintage%20Burma%20teak%20woodwork%20underneath.%20Look%20around%20and%20you%E2%80%99ll%20notice%20in%20some%20places%20the%20colours%20don%E2%80%99t%20quite%20match.%20Malik%20underscores%20that%20no%20attempts%20were%20made%20to%20polish%20the%20teak%20wood%20surfaces.%20This%20lends%20a%20rugged%2C%20raw%20touch%20to%20the%20staircase%20at%20the%20Native%20Restaurant%20and%20Bar%2C%20its%20roof%20structure%20and%20flooring%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Ice%20Factory%20roof%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20if%20there%20are%20mismatches%3F%20It%20only%20adds%20to%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20space%2C%20the%20architect%20believes.%20That%20being%20said%2C%20he%20adds%20that%20in%20places%20where%20it%20was%20necessitated%2C%20safety%20upgrades%20were%20made.%20These%20include%20structural%20reinforcements%20to%20the%20walls%20and%20roof.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg