r%20communities%20like%20Chingjaro%2C%20protecting%20the%20pangolin%20might%20as%20well%20be%20their%20first%20step%20into%20the%20conservation%20of%20their%20local%20wildlife.%20After%20all%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20the%20pangolins%20that%20ensure%20that%20the%20mountains%20of%20Manipur%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20written%20by%20Madhumay%20Mallik%20%E2%80%94%20a%20conservation%20writer%2C%20photographer%2C%20and%20graphic%20designer%2C%20currently%20engaged%20with%20the%20communications%20team%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wti.org.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWildlife%20Trust%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%3A%20Madhumay%20Mallik%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727177601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FFelicitating-community-leaders-of-Razai-Khullen-_-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727101616.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D367156%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amidst%20regional%20conflict%2C%20diverse%20communities%20in%20Manipur%20are%20coming%20together%2C%20recognising%20that%20protecting%20pangolins%20is%20vital%20for%20preserving%20biodiversity%20and%20ensuring%20a%20sustainable%20future%20for%20generations%20to%20come.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Guest%20Contributor%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F367156%2Fmanipur-pangolin-conservation-wildlife-trust-india-community-efforts-ecosystem-villages%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Foodies%20Share%207%20Must-Visit%20Spots%20in%20Jaipur%20for%20the%20Best%20Kachoris%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20think%20%3Cem%3Ekachoris%20%3C%2Fem%3E(deep-fried%20dough%20shells%20filled%20with%20a%20spicy%20mixture)%20are%2021st-century%20hype%2C%20you%20are%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E17th-century%20poet%20Banarasidas%20mentioned%20%E2%80%94%20in%20his%20poetic%20biographical%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EArdhakathanaka%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20snacking%20on%20these%20delights%20as%20far%20back%20as%201613%20in%20Indore.%20It%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20stretch%20to%20picture%20our%20ancestors%20binging%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F304840%2Fengineer-builds-online-marketplace-for-indian-mothers-to-sell-homemade-food-momskart%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ekachoris%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Echai%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewith%20the%20same%20gusto%20that%20the%20present%20generation%20does.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20a%20more%20popular%20theory%20about%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekachoris%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3Eorigins%20traces%20to%20the%20Marwari%20traders%20who%20presumably%20blended%20mild%20spices%20with%20dough%20to%20create%20this%20ingenious%20snack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlmost%20every%20region%20in%20India%20lays%20claim%20to%20the%20spicy%20stuffed%20pastry.%20While%20West%20Bengal%20calls%20itself%20the%20birthplace%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehing%20er%20kochuri%20ar%20aloo%20r%20dum%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20dish%20of%20potato%20and%20asafoetida-spiced%20%3Cem%3Ekachoris%3C%2Fem%3E)%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20interjects%20claiming%20that%20they%20were%20the%20first%20to%20come%20up%20with%20flattened%20balls%20with%20stuffing%20of%20%3Cem%3Emoong%20dal%3C%2Fem%3E%20(lentils)%2C%20which%20they%20say%20was%20the%20predecessor%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F263555%2Fbest-homemade-bihar-food-dishes-delhi-women-lockdown-business%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emodern-day%20%3Cem%3Ekachori%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20for%20now%2C%20let%E2%8