0rural%20communities%20across%20India%20through%20Hand%20in%20Hand%20India%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20day.%20A%20call%20from%20one%20of%20the%20children%20%E2%80%94%20informing%20her%20about%20a%20job%20they%20have%20secured%20or%20sharing%20a%20life%20event%20with%20her%20%E2%80%94%20manages%20to%20light%20up%20Dr%20Sankar%E2%80%99s%20mood.%20Point%20this%20out%20to%20her%20and%20she%20says%20it%20is%20all%20the%20validation%20she%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%20Meera%E2%80%99s%20story%20for%20instance.%20Meera%20was%20identified%20by%20the%20Child%20Labour%20Elimination%20Programme%20(CLEP)%20field%20staff%20in%202013.%20The%20family%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98scheduled%20tribe%E2%80%99%20status%20meant%20they%20were%20ostracised%20from%20society%20and%20Meera%20and%20her%20siblings%20were%20compelled%20to%20take%20up%20odd%20jobs%20%E2%80%94%20working%20at%20brick%20kilns%2C%20cutting%20forest%20wood%2C%20and%20grazing%20cattle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hand%20in%20Hand%20India%20team%20encouraged%20Meera%E2%80%99s%20parents%20to%20enrol%20her%20and%20her%20three%20siblings%20at%20the%20Dhamaneri%20Residential%20Special%20Training%20Centre%20(RSTC)%20in%20Tiruvallur%20district.%20The%20team%20then%20coaxed%20Meera%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359001%2Fias-officer-balika-panchayat-nanded-maharashtra-young-girls-fight-alcoholism-child-marriage%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomplete%20her%20studies%20%3C%2Fa%3Euntil%20Class%2012%2C%20providing%20her%20with%20all%20the%20necessary%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20she%20is%20a%20success%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStories%20like%20these%20underscore%20what%20Dr%20Sankar%20has%20been%20emphasising%20%E2%80%94%20one%E2%80%99s%20roots%20mustn%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20talent%20differentiator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHand%20in%20hand%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20remotest%20areas%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shelves%20in%20Dr%20Sankar%E2%80%99s%20office%20are%20heavy%20under%20the%20weight%20of%20her%20many%20accolades%C2%A0%20%E2%80%94%20a%20PhD%20in%20nuclear%20physics%3B%20the%20prestigious%20Lifetime%20Achievement%20Award%20in%20Financial%20Inclusion%20(2023)%20for%20her%20work%20in%20driving%20transformative%20socio-economic%20changes%20in%20the%20rural%20heartlands%20of%20North%20and%20South%20India%3B%20the%20Nari%20Shakti%20Puraskar%20(2016)%3B%20and%20the%20Global%20Award%20for%20Women%20Empowerment%20(2019)%20from%20UN%20Women%20and%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20Bahrain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20every%20undertaking%20is%20the%20desire%20to%20create%20an%20inclusion%20model%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20subscribe%20to%20convention.%20One%20that%20makes%20her%20most%20proud%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F63836%2Fchetna-gala-sinha-mann-deshi-mahila-bank%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancial%20inclusion%20model%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20able%20to%20provide%20financial%20inclusion%20to%20one%20million%20poor%20people.%20The%20fact%20that%20we%20have%20created%201.5%20million%20jobs%20is%20a%20testimonial%20to%20the%20hard%20work%20of%20my%20colleagues.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-6-1726670934.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Kalpana%20Sankar%20receiving%20an%20award%20from%20Former%20President%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsocial-development-6-1726670934.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%