glan-selfie-with-daughter-bibipur-village-haryana-daughters-day-women-empowerment-female-foeticide%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20a%20Couple%20Fought%20Relentless%20Battles%20to%20Demand%20Justice%20After%20Whistleblower%20Manjunath%E2%80%99s%20Murder%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETrigger%20warning%3A%20Mentions%20of%20murder%20and%20violence%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E1980s%2C%20Kolar%2C%20Karnataka%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20brothers%2C%20Manjunath%20and%20Raghavendra%20Shanmugam%2C%20were%20returning%20from%20school.%20As%20they%20chatted%2C%20Manjunath%20told%20his%20younger%20brother%20how%20he%20had%20stopped%20a%20classmate%20from%20bullying%20another%20student.%20This%20was%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20this%20young%20boy%20had%20dared%20to%20question%20what%20was%20clearly%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENovember%202005%2C%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20same%20righteous%20boy%20was%20now%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F307264%2Fgps-renewables-mainak-chakraborty-sreekrishna-sankar-ev-charging-station-biogas-to-electricity%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIIM%20graduate%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20and%20a%20sales%20officer%20at%20the%20Indian%20Oil%20Corporation%20(IOC).%20One%20of%20his%20responsibilities%20was%20checking%20petrol%20adulteration%20at%20petrol%20pumps.%20He%20set%20out%20on%20a%20tour%20of%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20district%20in%20November%202005.%20He%20found%20anomalies%2C%20for%20the%20second%20time%2C%20at%20the%20Mittal%20Automobile%20Petrol%20Pump%20and%20was%20about%20to%20take%20measures%20to%20seal%20it.%20On%20the%20night%20of%2019%20November%2C%20he%20was%20murdered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManjunath%E2%80%99s%20family%2C%20who%20were%20attending%20a%20family%20function%20in%20Chennai%2C%20were%20shocked%20beyon