ng%20the%20call%2C%E2%80%9D%20Anjali%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20480px)%20100vw%2C%20480px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fmanjunath-shan-1726829104.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Manjunath%20with%20his%20college%20friends%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fmanjunath-shan-1726829104.jpeg%20480w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fmanjunath-shan-1726829104-300x191.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fmanjunath-shan-1726829104-150x95.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366865%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22305%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EManjunath%20with%20his%20college%20friends.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20struggled%20to%20get%20him%20to%20testify.%20Until%20the%20day%20of%20the%20hearing%2C%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20if%20he%20would%20even%20show%20up%20to%20testify%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%2023%20March%2C%202007%20%E2%80%94%20after%20a%20trial%20of%20just%2010%20months%20%E2%80%94%20the%20verdict%20was%20pronounced%2C%20finding%20all%20eight%20accused%20guilty%20of%20murder.%20The%20main%20accused%2C%20Pawan%20Kumar%20Mittal%2C%20was%20sentenced%20to%20death%2C%20while%20the%20seven%20others%20were%20sentenced%20to%20life%20imprisonment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CI%20can%20now%20sleep%20in%20peace%2C%E2%80%9D%20were%20Manjunath%E2%80%99s%20mother%E2%80%99s%20words%20after%20the%20verdict.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20couple%20fought%20the%20case%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecuring%20justice%20was%20far%20from%20easy%2C%20and%20involved%20humongous%20efforts%20from%20the%20duo%20and%20the%20volunteers%20of%20the%20trust.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20how%20Anjali%20and%20Jaishankar%20ensured%20a%20fast-tracked%20trial%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETips%20to%20Fight%20a%20Court%20Case%20%26amp%3B%20Get%20Justice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EGet%20a%20good%20lawyer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20their%20contacts%2C%20the%20couple%20got%20a%20committed%2C%20skilled%2C%20and%20knowledgeable%20lawyer.%20According%20to%20the%20couple%2C%20having%20a%20senior%20lawyer%20who%20was%20completely%20committed%20to%20the%20case%20was%20a%20game-changer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EGet%20media%20attention%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20had%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20case%20stayed%20in%20the%20spotlight.%20So%2C%20Anjali%20and%20Jaishankar%20met%20with%20editors%20from%20various%20media%20organisations%2C%20who%20supported%20them%20by%20consistently%20reporting%20on%20the%20case.%20Anjali%20particularly%20mentions%20The%20Indian%20Express%20%E2%80%94%20who%20sent%20a%20reporter%20for%20every%20hearing%20%E2%80%94%20and%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%223%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuild%20pressure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20made%20sure%20the%20hearings%20weren%E2%80%99t%20delayed%20by%20getting%20letters%20from%20influential%20people%20like%20Narayana%20Murthy%20and%20Kris%20Gopalakrishnan%20of%20Infosys%20and%20senior%20IIM%20alumni%2C%20which%20they%20sent%20to%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%224%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBe%20present%20on%20the%20ground%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20every%20hearing%2C%20either%20Jaishankar%20or%20Anjali%20would%20travel%20from%20Mysuru%20to%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri.%20They%20would%20post%20the%20hearing%20dates%20in%20online%20alumni%20groups%3B%20alumni%20who%20were%20free%20on%20the%20date%2C%20would%20also%20attend.%20A%20group%20of%20IIM%20Lucknow%20student%20volunteers%20took%20turns%20to%20be%20present%20at%20the%20hearings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%225%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERaise%20funds%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20their%20extensive%20network%2C%20they%20were%20able%20to%20raise%20funds%20for%20all%20the%20legal%20and%20travel%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%226%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENever%20give%20up%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20importantly%2C%20despite%20the%20fight%20being%20solitary%20and%20difficult%2C%20they%20never%20lost%20hope.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Anjali%20and%20Jaishankar%2C%20travelled%20to%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20at%20least%2010%20times%20during%20the%20trial.%20Their%20journey%20involved%20taking%20a%20bus%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20a%20flight%20to%20Delhi%2C%20then%20to%20Lucknow%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20cab%20to%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20pushed%20them%20to%20fight%20for%20a%20boy%20they%20had%20never%20met%3F%20Didn%E2%80%99t%20they%20ever%20feel%20bogged%20down%3F%20%E2%80%9CCertainly.%20Some%20days%20were%20tough.%20At%20times%2C%20it%20seemed%20like%20an%20impossible%20task.%20We%20were%20carrying%20a%20heavy%20responsibility%20that%20we%20had%20to%20fulfil.%20We%20had%20to%20give%20our%20best%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Anjali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20IIM%20alumni%20volunteers%2C%20various%20people%20%E2%80%94%20complete%20strangers%20%E2%80%94%20wrote%20in%20and%20helped%2C%20which%20was%20a%20major%20support%2C%20they%20say.%20To%20honour%20his%20memory%2C%20on%20Manjunath%E2%80%99s%20first%20death%20anniversary%2C%20the%20trust%20inaugurated%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20Right%20To%20Information%20Act%20(RTI)%20helpline.%20The%20helpline%20ran%20for%20three%20years%2C%20helping%20thousands%20of%20citizens%20use%20the%20act%20to%20fight%20corruption.%20They%20also%20established%20the%20Manjunath%20Shanmugam%20Integrity%20Award%20to%20honour%20individuals%20who%20fought%20against%20systemic%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20fight%20for%20justice%20continued%20until%202015%2C%20as%20the%20convicts%20appealed%20in%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20in%202009%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202015.%20While%20the%20High%20Court%20upheld%20the%20convictions%2C%20it%20commuted%20Mittal%E2%80%99s%20death%20sentence%20to%20life%20imprisonment.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20upheld%20the%20convictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Believe%20that%20the%20system%20works%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20immersing%20yourself%20in%20a%20case%20like%20this%20for%20so%20long%2C%20life%20changes.%20One%E2%80%99s%20perspective%20towards%20life%20evolves%2C%20and%20for%20Anjali%20and%20Jaishankar%2C%20it%20was%20no%20different.%20While%20they%20had%20always%20been%20straightforward%20people%2C%20this%20experience%20made%20them%20even%20more%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-1726828969.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20tips%20to%20be%20a%20good%20citizen%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-1726828969.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-1726828969-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-1726828969-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-1726828969-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-1726828969-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366862%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20the%20easy%20way%20out%20was%20never%20an%20option%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBelieve%20that%20the%20system%20works.%20It%20might%20seem%20intimidating%20or%20impossible%20to%20get%20something%20done%20in%20a%20government%20institution%2C%20but%20believe%20me%2C%20it%20is%20possible.%20We%20did%20not%20pay%20even%20a%20single%20rupee%20as%20a%20bribe%2C%20and%20we%20got%20it%20done.%20It%20will%20take%20time%2C%20but%20you%20first%20have%20to%20decide%20that%20you%20will%20not%20take%20the%20shortcut%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jaishankar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20set%20up%20an%20edtech%20firm%20in%202009.%20Even%20in%20their%20corporate%20lives%2Cthey%20ensured%20that%20they%20lived%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F345065%2Fhow-to-find-a-lawyer-legal-startup-pune-shreya-sharma-divorce-family-court-business-property-law-rent-agreement%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EManjunath%E2%80%99s%20ideals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20even%20if%20it%20meant%20slower%20progress.They%20remained%20humble%20and%20stayed%20away%20from%20the%20limelight.%20All%20they%20want%20people%20to%20realise%20from%20their%20fight%20is%20that%20each%20of%20us%20can%20take%20small%20steps%20toward%20living%20a%20life%20of%20integrity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThree%20tips%20to%20be%20a%20good%20citizen%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EStand%20up%20and%20take%20action%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20time%20you%20sit%20in%20front%20of%20the%20television%20and%20complain%20about%20the%20system%2C%20think%20of%20Manjunath.%20Instead%20of%20just%20venting%2C%20take%20some%20action.%20It%20could%20be%20something%20as%20small%20as%20tweeting%20about%20a%20pothole%20to%20the%20local%20administration.%20There%20is%20a%20chance%20that%20it%20might%20spur%20action.%20Always%20raise%20your%20voice%20against%20injustice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20philosopher%20Edmund%20Burke%20once%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20thing%20necessary%20for%20the%20triumph%20of%20evil%C2%A0%20is%20for%20good%20men%20to%20do%20nothing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBe%20ethical%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20we%20aren%E2%80%99t%20directly%20paying%20bribes%2C%20many%20of%20us%20hire%20agents%20or%20brokers%20who%20do%20it%20on%20our%20behalf.%20Anjali%20advises%2C%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20go%20out%20of%20your%20way%20to%20bribe.%20If%20you%20break%20a%20traffic%20signal%2C%20pay%20the%20fine%2C%20not%20the%20cop.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%223%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHelp%20those%20in%20need%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20our%20responsibility%20to%20create%20a%20more%20equitable%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Anjali.%20Instead%20of%20looking%20up%20to%20those%20who%20are%20more%20privileged%2C%20focus%20on%20the%20millions%20living%20in%20poverty%20and%20do%20your%20part%20to%20help%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYour%20small%20contribution%20can%20make%20a%20big%20difference%20in%20someone%E2%80%99s%20life.%20Give%20whatever%20you%20can%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20Rs%201%2C000%20or%20Rs%2010%2C000.%20It%E2%80%99s%20important%20for%20your%20own%20peace%20of%20mind%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20Anjali%20and%20Jaishankar%20remain%20modest%20about%20their%20efforts%2C%20the%20Shanmugam%20family%20is%20deeply%20grateful%20to%20them.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20dedicated%20their%20lives%20for%20us.%20God%20comes%20in%20different%20forms.%20Everyone%20who%20came%20forward%20to%20help%2C%20motivate%2C%20and%20console%20us%2C%20including%20Manjunath%E2%80%99s%20friends%20and%20juniors%2C%20were%20manifestations%20of%20God.%20They%20showed%20me%20that%20there%20are%20good%20people%20in%20society%2C%20to%20balance%20out%20the%20bad%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Raghavendra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20showed%20the%20country%20that%20all%20it%20takes%20is%20for%20one%20person%20to%20take%20charge%20and%20act.%20Instead%20of%20merely%20making%20this%20case%20a%20dinner%20table%20conversation%2C%20they%20went%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20fought.%20All%20it%20takes%20is%20that%20first%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20will%20be%20your%20first%20step%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Raghavendra%20Shanmugam%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726842542000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-1-1726828603.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D366845%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20IOC%20officer%20Manjunath%20Shanmugam%20was%20murdered%20for%20exposing%20petrol%20adulteration%2C%20his%20IIM%20alumni%2C%20Anjali%20and%20Jaishankar%2C%20refused%20to%20stay%20silent.%20Taking%20action%20into%20their%20own%20hands%2C%20they%20fought%20a%20relentless%20legal%20battle%2C%20ensuring%20all%20the%20accused%20were%20convicted%20and%20justice%20was%20served.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F366845%2Fmanjunath-shanmugam-kolar-lakhimpur-kheri-karnataka-uttar-pradesh-anjali-mullatti-jaishankar-iim-ioc-